Install Postman tool
Use following APIs

1] When direct expiry date is not available and calculated on manufacturing date and expired time
Post : http://localhost:8080/calculateExpiryWithoutExpDate
Body param: manufactureDate : any date (02/14/2021)
expiresInDays: Any Int (30)



2] When Direct expired date is available
Post http://localhost:8080/calculateExpiry
Body Param: expiryDate :06/14/2021
